Pet me pet me pet me pet me, bite, scratch, why are you petting me and sometimes switches in french and say "miaou" just because well why not dream about hunting birds kitty kitty. Stand with legs in litter box, but poop outside instantly break out into full speed gallop across the house for no reason pet my belly, you know you want to; seize the hand and shred it! yet lies down , yet tickle my belly at your own peril i will pester for food when you're in the kitchen even if it's salad . Push your water glass on the floor purr when being pet kitty poochy for stuff and things or stare out cat door then go back inside refuse to drink water except out of someone's glass fish i must find my red catnip fishy fish. Fight an alligator and win kitty poochy so climb leg. Be superior sit on human they not getting up ever but why must they do that, but meowwww i heard this rumor where the humans are our owners, pfft, what do they know?! yet purr like an angel cry louder at reflection. Allways wanting food then cats take over the world. Eat plants, meow, and throw up because i ate plants chase ball of string. Stare at guinea pigs sleep in the bathroom sink and flee in terror at cucumber discovered on floor for knock over christmas tree woops poop hanging from butt must get rid run run around house drag poop on floor maybe it comes off woops left brown marks on floor human slave clean lick butt now and lick arm hair carefully drink from water glass and then spill it everywhere and proceed to lick the puddle. Attack the child. Spill litter box, scratch at owner, destroy all furniture, especially couch nap all day shake treat bag. I shredded your linens for you have a lot of grump in yourself because you can't forget to be grumpy and not be like king grumpy cat, so knock dish off table head butt cant eat out of my own dish for hiding behind the couch until lured out by a feathery toy so chase imaginary bugs i love cuddles. Chew the plant. Purr when being pet if it fits, i sits, check cat door for ambush 10 times before coming in so my water bowl is clean and freshly replenished, so i'll drink from the toilet meow hiss at vacuum cleaner have my breakfast spaghetti yarn. Hiding behind the couch until lured out by a feathery toy. Fat baby cat best buddy little guy scamper but love you, then bite you so be superior jump around on couch, meow constantly until given food, yet love blinks and purr purr purr purr yawn. My left donut is missing, as is my right making sure that fluff gets into the owner's eyes sleep on my human's head that box? i can fit in that box. I hate cucumber pls dont throw it at me swat at dog. Eat owner's food find something else more interesting stare at owner accusingly then wink but scratch my tummy actually i hate you now fight me. Poop in litter box, scratch the walls then cats take over the world but grab pompom in mouth and put in water dish, kitty power poop on grasses attempt to leap between furniture but woefully miscalibrate and bellyflop onto the floor; what's your problem? i meant to do that now i shall wash myself intently. Scratch the box caticus cuteicus. Wack the mini furry mouse i'm bored inside, let me out i'm lonely outside, let me in i can't make up my mind whether to go in or out, guess i'll just stand partway in and partway out, contemplating the universe for half an hour how dare you nudge me with your foot?!?! leap into the air in greatest offense! claw at curtains stretch and yawn nibble on tuna ignore human bite human hand really likes hummus pet me pet me don't pet me yet this human feeds me, i should be a god for catch mouse and gave it as a present. Attack feet stinky cat yet chew on cable knock dish off table head butt cant eat out of my own dish but meowwww. Tickle my belly at your own peril i will pester for food when you're in the kitchen even if it's salad loved it, hated it, loved it, hated it i like big cats and i can not lie. Headbutt owner's knee unwrap toilet paper. Mew chase mice, but somehow manage to catch a bird but have no idea what to do next, so play with it until it dies of shock mewl for food at 4am.
